--
To play nim run the Nim program and choose first size of the heap, and the max size that a hand can be.
The computer will then randomly decide who gets to start.
Take turns with the computer player taking a number between 1 and the maximum hand specified earlier.
The person to takes the last object from the heap is the winner.
The computer will annouce the winner and also note who should've won, as the initial conditions of nim gurentees a winner if
the player knows the proper algorithm.
--
have fun!
